lion views. He recently launched Mr. Beast Burger [ https://substack.com/re=
direct/c2e26748-4522-4710-a9f6-ff48b6cc9dde?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7G=
nA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] and Feastables [ https://substack.com=
