The second was Patrick O=E2=80=99Shaughnessy=E2=80=99s conversation with Gr=
avity Blanket creator John Fio on Invest Like the Best:=C2=A0
The whole conversation is worth listening to =E2=80=93 I=E2=80=99d never he=
