=2Egb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8Ex=
kRNpU" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #404=
040; text-decoration: underline;">Write of Passage</a><span> course on Twit=
ter, I signed up.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The course worked. It for=
ced me to write every week, gave me a community of people who were also try=
