d; line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><stro=
ng>Differentiation Matters More Than Ever</strong></h3><p style=3D"color: #=
404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So why am =
I writing about this now?&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 1=
6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>When I first thought abo=
ut writing this essay, I planned to go deep on all of the unexpected ways d=
ifferentiation matters for </span><strong>startups</strong><span>, based in=
